sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AuthHandler as Auth Handler
    participant AuthUC as Auth Use Case
    participant UserRepo as User Repository
    participant JWT as JWT Token Service
    participant Router as REST Router
    participant RBAC as RBAC Middleware
    participant ACL as ACL Checker
    participant Handler as Protected Handler

    Client->>AuthHandler: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    AuthHandler->>AuthUC: Login(ctx, credentials)
    AuthUC->>UserRepo: FindByEmail(ctx, email)
    UserRepo-->>AuthUC: user with roles
    AuthUC->>AuthUC: verify password
    AuthUC->>JWT: GenerateTokenPair(...)
    JWT-->>AuthUC: access and refresh tokens
    AuthUC-->>AuthHandler: auth output
    AuthHandler-->>Client: 200 OK with tokens

    Client->>Router: request protected endpoint with Bearer token
    Router->>JWT: ValidateToken(ctx, token)
    JWT-->>Router: token claims
    Router->>RBAC: RequirePermission(resource, action)
    RBAC-->>Router: role-based decision

    alt resource-specific access required
        Router->>ACL: check subject access to resource
        ACL-->>Router: allow or deny
    end

    Router->>Handler: request with claims in context
    Handler-->>Client: success or domain error response
